title: Purina Pro Plan Complete Essentials Wet Dog Food Chicken and Rice Entree and Beef and Rice Entree Variety Pack - (Pack of 12) 13 oz. Cans
description: Savor your dog's happiness when you give him a selection from this Purina Pro Plan COMPLETE ESSENTIALS Classic adult wet dog food variety pack. Real chicken or beef is the number1ingredient in this Purina dog food, and each super-premium dog food entree is made with high-quality ingredients, including highly digestible rice. Skin-nourishing nutrients in every dog wet food serving support your dog's healthy skin and coat, while the high protein level helps to promote his ideal body condition. Each selection in this canned dog food variety pack contains no artificial colors, flavors or preservatives. Our high protein wet dog food formulas help build lean muscles while supporting his healthy immune system. Your dog gets 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for adult dogs in every bowl. Rotate between the two mouthwatering entrees offered in this Purina Pro Plan COMPLETE ESSENTIALS premium wet dog food variety pack to keep your dog intrigued.
